title: The Anthony Cumia Show 2014-09-03 (MP4)
description:
Wednesday, September 3, 2014

Anthony starts Wednesday's show by recapping Jim Norton's visit and with Ray Liotta calling in to discuss how he's managed to stay out of tabloids and his new film, "The Identical." He then takes a few listener calls, talks about the difference between men and women when it comes to nude leaks, and about how unsafe the iCloud is. He shows us a "fuck her right in the pussy" shout out video, a video of possibly the worst comic ever, one of a "know it all" in a courthouse, and Keith tells us about the first time he used a Taser. Ant gets into Rat's lack of a past, tells us how the conversation really goes down in the gaming community, and he examines using your real name versus being anonymous online. Ant introduces us to a TV show called "Girlfriend Intervention" as well as a new Snoop Dogg video and the double standards surrounding them, and then FINALLY, Beavis makes an appearance. He ends today by talking about a "freak show" on TLC and by braving a few more calls.
